results.description: Cause of death unknown. Found by KFT Rangers. Kenya Horned Viper or Puff Adder (seems too high altitude)

comments.body: Thanks! I thought you might like that one...
Wow, thanks for contributing this to iNat @mossambica, it's iNaturalist's Observation of the Day! We've posted it to our Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram accounts.
Holy smokes - that's a species you don't see every day!! Congratulations!
Congrats on the first. Made your image the taxon photo.

My what a beautiful snake! 

I am not a snake fan but this is a pretty cool snake!!

wow that's an awesome one!

@bobbyfingers @michael_jacobi @wolfgang_wuster check it out
